mainText:
Dear Steve, 
Tonight I must tell you that every product you made I worshipped it and after every presentation I would make at work  I would put my Apple logo in the end on keynotes to tell the Non Mac world that I am proud of my mac.
I will miss you immensely. It is painful to think we will not see you again but  you will always be with us in every product you ever made.&nbsp;
